                            <comment id="242967" author="pjones" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2019 18:08:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The exact timing depends on testing results but I would hope that the release is out within a couple of weeks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="242964" author="cmcl" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2019 17:33:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Peter. I am not sure whether it is actually causing an issue for our workloads. I&apos;m hoping we can go for the official release - any idea roughly on&#160; when it will hit the street?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cheers,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Campbell&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="242961" author="pjones" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2019 15:19:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Campbell&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think that the issue is that you are carrying the patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11647&quot; title=&quot;niobuf.c:330:ptlrpc_register_bulk()) ASSERTION( desc-&amp;gt;bd_md_count == 0 ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11647&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11647&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; which also needs this patch - &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/34027/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/34027/&lt;/a&gt;&#160;. We are putting the finishing touches to 2.10.7 which should have everything that you need. Even if you decide to patch immediately I would definitely recommend upgrading to the official release once it becomes available.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="242951" author="cmcl" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2019 13:33:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Corresponding messages on the MDS:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Feb 24 13:20:05 fmds1 kernel: Lustre: 10400:0:(mdt_handler.c:5340:mdt_connect_internal()) foxtrot-MDT0000: client foxtrot-MDT0000-lwp-OST0007_UUID does not support ibits lock, either very old or an invalid client: flags 0x2041401043000020&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="242949" author="cmcl" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2019 13:16:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry, forgot versions:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.10.6.2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This has patches as per&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11826&quot; title=&quot;Cannot send after transport endpoint shutdown&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11826&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11826&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11693&quot; title=&quot;Soft lockups on Lustre clients&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11693&quot;&gt;LU-11693&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Kernel is&#160;kernel-3.10.0-514.el7_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
